HEADWORD: Disbeliever
<hw>Dis`be*liev"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who
disbelieves, or refuses belief; an unbeliever. Specifically, one who
does not believe the Christian religion.</def> <rj><au>I.
Watts.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

